TITLE: Defining ZModel Schema with tRPC Plugin
DESCRIPTION: Example of a ZModel schema file with tRPC plugin configuration and model definitions for a blogging app.
SOURCE: https://github.com/zenstackhq/zenstack-docs/blob/main/docs/reference/plugins/trpc.md#2025-04-10_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: zmodel
