TITLE: Adding Access Policies to Post Model in ZModel
DESCRIPTION: Enhanced Post model with ZenStack access policies for tenant isolation. Defines who can read, create, update, and delete posts based on ownership and space membership.
SOURCE: https://github.com/zenstackhq/zenstack-docs/blob/main/blog/multi-tenant/index.md#2025-04-10_snippet_4

