TITLE: Using ZenStack with Cloudflare Workers and Neon Database
DESCRIPTION: Example of implementing ZenStack in a Cloudflare Workers environment with a Neon database. This code demonstrates how to use the correct edge imports and create a database connection for each request in a serverless function.
SOURCE: https://github.com/zenstackhq/zenstack-docs/blob/main/docs/guides/edge.md#2025-04-10_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: typescript
