TITLE: Defining Post Model with Access Policies in ZenStack
DESCRIPTION: This ZModel schema defines a Post model with access policies that allow the author full access to their posts, while allowing all authenticated users to read published posts. It also sets up automatic user association through the createdById field.
SOURCE: https://github.com/zenstackhq/zenstack-docs/blob/main/docs/quick-start/nextjs-app-router.mdx#2025-04-10_snippet_15

