TITLE: Component Lookup for Polymorphic Rendering
DESCRIPTION: Using a component lookup dictionary to dynamically select the appropriate component based on the contentType field, reducing conditional rendering logic.
SOURCE: https://github.com/zenstackhq/zenstack-docs/blob/main/blog/ocp/index.md#2025-04-10_snippet_14

LANGUAGE: tsx
CODE:
```
const componentLookup: {
  [key: string]: (content: { content: Content }) => JSX.Element;
} = {
  Post,
  Image
  // Add other components here...
};

const PolymorphicContent = ({
  componentName,
  content,
}: {
  componentName: string;
  content: Content;
}) => {
  const Component = componentLookup[componentName];
  return Component ? <Component content={content} /> : null;
};
```

