SOURCE: https://github.com/zenstackhq/zenstack-docs/blob/main/docs/the-complete-guide/part1/4-access-policy/4.3-current-user.md#2025-04-10_snippet_6

LANGUAGE: zmodel
CODE:
```
model Post {
    ...
    author User @relation(fields: [authorId], references: [id])
    authorId Int
    @@allow('update', auth() == author)
}

// Equivalent to:
model Post {
    ...
    author User @relation(fields: [authorId], references: [id])
    authorId Int
    @@allow('update', auth().id == author.id)
}

// Also equivalent to:
model Post {
    ...
    author User @relation(fields: [authorId], references: [id])
    authorId Int
    @@allow('update', auth().id == authorId)
}
```

