TITLE: Mounting ZenStack API in SvelteKit Server Hooks
DESCRIPTION: TypeScript code for creating a SvelteKit server hooks file to mount the ZenStack API. It includes setting up an enhanced Prisma client with user context and configuring the SvelteKitHandler.
